<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; background: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .wrapper { max-width: 520px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; overflow: hidden; }
      .header { background: #0ea5e9; padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
      .body { padding: 32px; }
      .body p { line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; color: #374151; }
      .household { background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .household p { margin: 0; color: #0369a1; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; }
      .role-badge { display: inline-block; background: #e0f2fe; color: #0369a1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 99px; margin-top: 6px; text-transform: capitalize; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 8px 0 20px; }
      .url-fallback { word-break: break-all; color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px; }
      .expiry { font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; }
      .footer { padding: 20px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: center; }
      .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🐱 CatCare</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <p>Hi there,</p>
        <p><strong><%= @invited_by %></strong> has invited you to join their household on CatCare.</p>
        <div class="household">
          <p><%= @household_name %></p>
          <span class="role-badge"><%= @role %></span>
        </div>
        <p>Click the button below to accept your invitation and get started. This link expires in <strong>7 days</strong>.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="<%= @invite_url %>" class="btn">Accept invitation</a>
        </p>
        <p>Or copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
        <p class="url-fallback"><%= @invite_url %></p>
        <p class="expiry">If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>CatCare &mdash; Helping you care for your feline friends</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
